Dear Student,

Congratulations and welcome to LearnHub!

We are excited to have you join our learning community of over 2 million students worldwide. Your enrollment has been confirmed and your account is now active.

GETTING STARTED:

  1. Access Your Student Dashboard
     View your enrolled courses, upcoming deadlines, and progress reports.
     https://app.learnhub.edu/dashboard

  2. Explore Your Courses
     Your enrolled courses are ready and waiting for you.
     https://app.learnhub.edu/my-courses

  3. Meet Your Instructors
     Introduce yourself in the course community forums.
     https://app.learnhub.edu/community

  4. Download the LearnHub App
     Learn on the go — even offline — with our mobile app.
     https://app.learnhub.edu/mobile

  5. Set Your Learning Goals
     Use our goal tracker to stay on top of your studies.
     https://app.learnhub.edu/goals

YOUR STUDENT RESOURCES:
  - Academic Support: support@learnhub.edu
  - Technical Help: techhelp@learnhub.edu
  - Student Helpdesk: +91 90000 22222 (Mon–Fri, 9 AM – 6 PM IST)
  - Help Center: https://help.learnhub.edu

Tips for Success:
  * Set aside dedicated study time each day
  * Participate actively in discussion forums
  * Reach out to your instructor whenever you have questions
  * Take advantage of our live doubt-clearing sessions every week

We believe in your potential and are here to support you every step of the way!

Best wishes,
The LearnHub Team
www.learnhub.edu
welcome@learnhub.edu

